name: Selana
content: Selana was a female Human who served as a lieutenant with the Oquan, a bounty hunter group that operated on the planet Naalol. During the time of the Galactic Civil War, the Rebel Alliance procurement officer Lieutenant Talnar crash-landed on Naalol and the Oquan planned to capture him, so that they could sell him to the Galactic Empire. Selana and the Oquan lieutenant Patch subsequently led a group of 15 Oquan that subdued Talnar and took him captive.
